    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and the interior is clean with only minor wear on the driver's seat. While the exterior paint still has a great shine, there are a few small stone chips on the hood and some light scuffing on the rear bumper consistent with regular use. It\u2019s a reliable, solid car that\u2019s ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
