      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Unlock the potential of this diamond in the rough! This vehicle is in poor condition and is the perfect project for a dedicated restorer or someone looking for a budget-friendly parts car. It\u2019s ready for a complete overhaul, offering a fantastic opportunity to roll up your sleeves and bring a vehicle back to life!",
